db.col.aggregate(
    [
        {
            $match: {

            }
        }
    ]
);

- used to filter data
- can be used multiple time
- many stages can come after it
- uses query operators except for $where
- if we want to use $text, it has to be the first stage in the pipeline
- can't use aggregation expressions

db.col.count({ predicate });
db.col.countDocuments({ predicate });
db.col.estimatedDocumentCount({ predicate });

